text: Sen. Rand Paul is the first senator to test positive for COVID-19. He's also one of eight Republican senators who voted against a coronavirus relief package last week. https://t.co/RSpc50KvmP

urls.title: Sen. Rand Paul Has Tested Positive For The Coronavirus
